AddressInfo.Title: Mall of the South (Alberton)
AddressInfo.AddressLine1: Cnr Swartkoppies and Kliprivier Drive, Aspen Lakes Ext 2
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Main Entry Point	
From Swartkoppies Road, take the slipway and continue to the round-about. Enter through the boom and continue straight. Take the second turn to your left to the basement parking area. Drive straight towards the entrance, Drive to the right of the entrance, past the parking bays into the corner. The charge point is situated against the wall right to the entrance. - From Swartkoppies Road, take the slipway and continue to the round-about. Enter through the boom and continue straight.
